{
  "stem": "4187.1",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we-- we noticed that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But-- yeah, we remarked on it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know, what are all these planes up there?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Anyway, then we went to mass.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And when we came out, honestly, without actually seeing anything, the atmosphere, there was something so different.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we couldn't-- we didn't know, what is it?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "What's happening?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then we realized that what we're hearing, from a certain distance, was thump, thump, thump, Germans marching.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, the-- the-- the columns was-- were marching somewhere down, I don't know how-- how many streets down, wherever.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we could hear this thump, thump, thump.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it was-- it was frightening.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was-- well, it was so strange, of course.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then slowly, the-- we started hearing the motorized transport.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It-- they must have, I guess, just reached the center of town or, you know, our area.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because there-- there was this-- this incredible changed atmosphere.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And so we-- we went-- we went-- went home, of course.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There was my father and my mother.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Both of them are like they were different people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They were white as-- as a sheet.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they told us that we've got to face very difficult times, because the Germans have marched in.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And it means, to us-- not that they would have pointed out what it actually meant to us.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I don't think they knew that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Well, in fact, I'm sure they didn't.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Because my father was offered a chair in-- in one of the US universities in 193-- '39, 1940, and he didn't accept it.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Because he said he can't-- he can't do this to his family and, you know, to-- to uproot everyone.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And, also, because he truly believed that, no matter what, it-- nothing's going to happen to his family because-- because of him.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
